DART's "dart" collision detector supports ray intersection since the native
engine consolidation (raycast merged in dartsim/dart#3355; the consolidated
engine became the "dart" key and the default in 6.20). Move "dart" from the
unsupported to the supported ray-intersection detectors; the supported test's
analytic sphere assertions (hit point, normal, fraction 0.25) pass unchanged.
Line numbers assume gz-physics8-changed-world-poses.patch is applied first
(patches apply in filename order).

